The paper proposes a method for designing multi-task deep learning architectures and evaluates it on person attributes classification tasks involving facial and clothing attributes. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and multimedia (cs.MM).
